  "description": "¶25th Spirit of the Ars Goetia Rank: President and Earl\nLegions Commanded: 36\n¶Classical Attributes (per Ars Goetia): “He is a Mighty President and Earl, appearing in the form of a dog with wings like a griffin. He teacheth all arts in an instant, and is the author and captain of all manslaughters and bloodshed. He teacheth all things past and to come. He causeth the love of friends and foes. He can make men invisible and is an excellent familiar. He governeth 36 legions of spirits.”\n",
